10. Enter Body Content
11. Click Save button
12. Verify new post created successfully
(sees message 'New post successfully created.', see title and body content)
13. Click on Edit button
14. Change title
15. Change Content Body
16. Click on Save button
17. Check that message 'Post successfully updated.' is appear
18. Click on Back to post permalink button

Expected Result:
19. Verify new post updated successfully
(see new title and body content)